ừ - 秋風辭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tri%E1%BB%87t/author-gLGd-Bchdqe6FBWqpEd9Qw">Lưu Triệt</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Th%E1%BB%A9-C%C3%BAc-Pha-t%E1%BA%B7ng-thi/poem-gxa3FX0q9ruPHHzMRC6NJw">Thứ Cúc Pha tặng thi - 次菊坡贈詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Nh%E1%BA%ADn/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Linh-kh%C3%BAc-ho%E1%BA%A1-T%E1%BB%AD-T%C3%A1i-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-35vm9koP0o2qFN9Jq6m-0g">Tương Linh khúc hoạ Tử Tái vận - 湘靈曲和子載韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Nh%E1%BA%ADn/author-iAOn3uaLIlAHhHS3XAcQ1g">Uông Nhận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/Y%C3%AAn-%C4%91%C3%A0i-thi-H%E1%BA%A1/poem-p6so07bCwHh5_6fH3dXTig">Yên đài thi - Hạ - 燕臺詩－夏</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
